choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for seven days.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
Day 1: Grilled chicken breast with quinoa and steamed vegetables (broccoli, carrots, zucchini)
Day 2: Baked salmon with sweet potato and green beans
Day 3: Turkey meatballs with spaghetti squash and roasted Brussels sprouts
Day 4: Grilled shrimp skewers with brown rice and mixed vegetables (bell peppers, onions, mushrooms)
Day 5: Lentil soup with whole wheat bread and a side salad of cucumber and tomatoes
Day 6: Baked tofu with cauliflower rice and stir-fried vegetables (bok choy, bell peppers, onions)
Day 7: Grilled chicken breast with quinoa and roasted Brussels sprouts
